{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"1143","heading":"Grants","label":"1143 Grants","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1143","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/ch22/schIII","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs1143","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextThe Magnuson-Stevens Fishery Conservation and Management Act, referred to in subsec. (f)(3), is , , , which is classified principally to chapter 38 (§ 1801 et seq.) of Title 16, Conservation. Title III of the Act is classified generally to subchapter IV (§ 1851 et seq.) of chapter 38 of Title 16. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under and Tables.Pub. L. 94–26590 Stat. 331section 1801 of Title 16Apr. 13, 1976","CodificationSection was enacted as part of the Young Fishermen’s Development Act, and not as part of titles I and II of which comprise this chapter.Pub. L. 89–454"],"amendments":["References in TextThe Magnuson-Stevens Fishery Conservation and Management Act, referred to in subsec. (f)(3), is , , , which is classified principally to chapter 38 (§ 1801 et seq.) of Title 16, Conservation. Title III of the Act is classified generally to subchapter IV (§ 1851 et seq.) of chapter 38 of Title 16. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under and Tables.Pub. L. 94–26590 Stat. 331section 1801 of Title 16Apr. 13, 1976"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"In general","label":"a In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1143/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1143","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs1143%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1143/a/1","parentIdentifier":